{
  "stem": "21812.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- this was the idea of Secretary of War Stimson who created this thing because he felt that after the war, we would be marching into Vienna.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Archduke Otto and his brother would be marching in front of us and reestablish the old Austrian-Hungarian monarchy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very little is known about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so the newspaper created an enormous stink.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And eventually they decided they'd have to disband the battalion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was an infantry battalion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we trained during the winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was pretty rough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they gave us a choice of either to-- they didn't disband it yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What they did was, you had a choice, which was amazing for the Army, I think the only time it ever happened, of either going-- staying or getting into a regular infantry division.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you know why they decided to disband that idea?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was so much adverse publicity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the climate was-- at that point, was so much against monarchies and establishing the old order, I guess, whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyway, so 75% of the people signed up to get out, and-- because it was the weirdest thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were university professors with four degrees, four doctoral degrees, in that battalion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there were peasant farmers from Yugoslavia or from wherever, Herzegovina, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] totally illiterate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was the-- the weirdest kind of combination.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was dying to get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- I got shipped into the 75th Infantry Division at Fort Leonard Wood, Missouri.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I tried to get into-- into intelligence, into the intelligence, Army intelligence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in that camp was a friend of my uncle's who had-- who was in intelligence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was too late already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had filled up the intelligence quota, and I couldn't get into it.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
